{"tid":205731,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"睇過風夏嘅吾該入一入黎","createTime":"2017-04-18T04:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T15:26:29.000Z","uid":102208,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d08aff737258abfa169ca0ab5a8e1adbe11b46c","tid":205731,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"我正式宣布 我要屌鳩作者同男主老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啱啱睇哂動畫，睇到成肚火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解男主揀風夏都唔揀小雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明一齊得咁好都要出軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁都唔係最嬲<br />\n最嬲係男主玩弄小雪對佢嘅感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連小雪投懷送抱都無動於衷<br />\n一句對唔住就咩都唔理<br />\n咁樣對得住小雪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未試過睇動漫睇到咁嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc96dab328ef3c8f36e39ba2dd0c20202945f044","tid":205731,"uid":102208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T04:02:54.000Z","msg":"之後我就即刻極速睇漫畫睇下咩情況<br />\n我hi<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">人都死左仲要搞其他風夏</span></span><br />\n男主依然唔接受小雪嘅表白<br />\n希望作者比多一次機會小雪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf719b5df826231ca367b412c4a5fa58ee429174","tid":205731,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"064f5364371a7eeadb9e672a6db291111257daea","tid":205731,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T04:05:14.000Z","msg":"搵二號機就知on9"},{"pid":"58d8a5f4deef399b8b7059968ff73280fdb28789","tid":205731,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2